## 為什麼
- 防暴力破解密碼
- 防 API abuse
- 防 DDoS

## Express + express-rate-limit
```javascript
import rateLimit from "express-rate-limit";

const limiter = rateLimit({
  windowMs: 15 * 60 * 1000,
  max: 100
});

app.use("/api", limiter);

// 登入更嚴
app.post("/api/login", rateLimit({
  windowMs: 15 * 60 * 1000,
  max: 5
}), loginHandler);
```

## Redis 實作
```javascript
async function checkRateLimit(key, max, windowSec) {
  const count = await redis.incr(key);
  if (count === 1) await redis.expire(key, windowSec);
  if (count > max) throw new Error("rate limited");
}

await checkRateLimit(`ratelimit:${userId}`, 100, 60);
```

## Cloudflare
- 免費 plan：基本 DDoS
- Pro：rate limit rules
- 一鍵搞定

## Next.js Middleware
```typescript
import { Ratelimit } from "@upstash/ratelimit";
import { Redis } from "@upstash/redis";

const ratelimit = new Ratelimit({
  redis: Redis.fromEnv(),
  limiter: Ratelimit.slidingWindow(10, "10 s")
});

export async function middleware(req) {
  const ip = req.ip ?? "127.0.0.1";
  const { success } = await ratelimit.limit(ip);
  if (!success) return new Response("Too many", { status: 429 });
}
```

## Response Headers
```javascript
res.setHeader("X-RateLimit-Limit", "100");
res.setHeader("X-RateLimit-Remaining", remaining);
res.setHeader("X-RateLimit-Reset", resetTimestamp);
```

## 分層
- 全域：1000/min
- 每 IP：100/min
- 每 user：50/min
- 敏感 endpoint：5/min

## CAPTCHA
觸發 rate limit 後：
- reCAPTCHA v3
- Cloudflare Turnstile（免費、推薦）
- hCaptcha

## 心法
- 登入：5 次失敗/15 分
- API：100/min
- AI / 重 endpoint：10/min
- 永遠回 429 + Retry-After

