## 同源
origin = protocol + domain + port
- `https://a.com` vs `https://api.a.com`：不同
- `http://` vs `https://`：不同

## CORS Headers
```
Access-Control-Allow-Origin: https://example.com
Access-Control-Allow-Methods: GET, POST, PUT, DELETE
Access-Control-Allow-Headers: Content-Type, Authorization
Access-Control-Allow-Credentials: true
```

## Express
```javascript
import cors from "cors";

app.use(cors({
  origin: "https://example.com",
  credentials: true
}));

// 多 origin
app.use(cors({
  origin: (origin, cb) => {
    const allowed = ["https://example.com", "https://app.example.com"];
    if (!origin || allowed.includes(origin)) cb(null, true);
    else cb(new Error("Not allowed"));
  }
}));
```

## Preflight
複雜 request 先送 OPTIONS、server 必須處理。

## Credentials
```javascript
// Frontend
fetch(url, { credentials: "include" });

// Backend：Allow-Origin 不能 *、要具體
```

## 常見錯誤
- ❌ Allow-Origin: * + Credentials
- ❌ 沒處理 OPTIONS
- ❌ Origin mismatch

## 安全
- 不要無腦 *
- 白名單具體 origin

## 心法
- Dev `*`、Production 白名單
- 不確定就 `cors` middleware
- 看瀏覽器 console 錯誤

