## 區別
- **Authentication**：「你是誰」→ 登入
- **Authorization**：「你能做什麼」→ 權限

## RBAC（Role-Based）
```typescript
const ROLES = {
  ADMIN: ["read", "write", "delete"],
  EDITOR: ["read", "write"],
  VIEWER: ["read"]
};

function can(user, action) {
  return ROLES[user.role].includes(action);
}
```

## ABAC（Attribute-Based）
```typescript
function can(user, action, resource) {
  if (action === "edit" && resource.owner_id === user.id) return true;
  if (user.role === "admin") return true;
  return false;
}
```

## Middleware
```typescript
function requireRole(role) {
  return (req, res, next) => {
    if (req.user.role !== role) return res.status(403).end();
    next();
  };
}

app.delete("/admin/users/:id", requireRole("admin"), deleteUser);
```

## 資源層級
```typescript
async function canEditPost(user, postId) {
  const post = await db.post.findUnique({ where: { id: postId } });
  return post.user_id === user.id || user.role === "admin";
}
```

## PG RLS
DB 層級 authorization：
```sql
ALTER TABLE posts ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
CREATE POLICY "own_posts" ON posts
FOR ALL USING (user_id = auth.uid());
```
Supabase 內建。

## Casl（JS）
```typescript
import { Ability } from "@casl/ability";

const ability = new Ability([
  { action: "read", subject: "Post" },
  { action: "update", subject: "Post", conditions: { user_id: user.id } }
]);

if (ability.can("update", post)) {}
```

## IDOR 漏洞
```typescript
// ❌ 沒檢查擁有者
app.get("/api/posts/:id", (req, res) => {
  return db.post.findUnique({ where: { id: req.params.id } });
});

// ✅
app.get("/api/posts/:id", async (req, res) => {
  const post = await db.post.findUnique({ where: { id: req.params.id } });
  if (post.user_id !== req.user.id) return res.status(403).end();
  return post;
});
```

## 心法
- 永遠 server 做 authorization（前端只是 UX）
- RBAC 起手、需要再升 ABAC
- RLS 是雙保險

